				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				In response to the above post about the resistance of this spell by Aviaks: ALL Aviak Harriers are invulnerable to spells cast by someone under level 20 (spell does not have to be a lvl 20 spell, just the caster).  ALL Aviak Avocets resist spells under level 24.  The only spells that they can't resist are the Tashan series, which lower Magic Resistance and occasionally let a lvl 19 cast on Harriers or a 23 cast on Avocets, but it does not allow this often.  The Tashan series of spells are MEGA-TAUNTS! BE CAREFUL, ENCHANTERS!<BR>
